          <Comment>This variant is not present in population databases (ExAC no frequency). For these reasons, this variant has been classified as Pathogenic. ClinVar contains an entry for this variant (Variation ID: 1185049). This premature translational stop signal has been observed in individual(s) with Cornelia de Lange syndrome (PMID: 30716475, 32193685). This sequence change creates a premature translational stop signal (p.Glu315Glnfs*9) in the RAD21 gene. It is expected to result in an absent or disrupted protein product. Loss-of-function variants in RAD21 are known to be pathogenic (PMID: 22633399, 24378232, 27620904, 27882533).</Comment>
